        {
            "title": "倪樂琳首次演戲喊到抽離不到  被指撞樣「Rebecca」想做對方細妹  梁嘉莹被指最大懵王汛文想拍戲",
            "description": "<div class=\"video paragraphs medium\">\n<div id=\"vdo-player-container\">\n<video class=\"video-js vjs-default-skin\" controls=\"\" id=\"vdo-player\" muted=\"\" playsinline=\"\" poster=\"https://image.hkhl.hk/f/686e386/0x0/100/none/d2dac24422d47bdff6c1d05960a1c703/2025-04/misshkkkk.jpg\" width=\"100%\">\n<source src=\"https://video.hkhl.hk/50e7a216175171f0961e5014c1ca0102/83df451393df49909a63f1318b9af747-a0d48f116d0716a13fd8758f7e4e56ea-ld.mp4\" type=\"video/mp4\">\n                        Your browser does not support the video tag.\n                    </source></video>\n<div class=\"vdo-ad-container web\" data-vslot=\"vod_ad\" id=\"div-gpt-vad-67f9e9f51efac\"></div>\n<div class=\"vdo-ad-container mweb\" data-vslot0=\"vod_ad,2\" id=\"div-gpt-vad-67f9e9f51efae\"></div>\n</div>\n<p> <figure class=\"margin-top-1\">\n<img alt=\"倪樂琳首次演戲喊到抽離不到  被指撞樣「Rebecca」想做對方細妹  梁嘉莹被指最大懵王汛文想拍戲\" class=\"size-full w-100\" src=\"https://image.stheadline.com/f/680p0/0x0/100/none/e11bfcf2e4e3ab6e99d480a6adeca8cf/stheadline/inewsmedia/20250412/_2025041211465249230.jpg\"/>\n<figcaption class=\"caption-text\">倪樂琳首次演戲喊到抽離不到  被指撞樣「Rebecca」想做對方細妹  梁嘉莹被指最大懵王汛文想拍戲</figcaption>\n</figure>\n</p>\n<div class=\"in-article-banner\">\n<div class=\"mx-auto web\" data-slot=\"inarticlebanner,1,1\" id=\"inarticlebanner1\"></div>\n<div class=\"mx-auto mweb\" data-slot=\"inarticlebanner,1,2\" id=\"inarticlebanner1-MWeb\"></div>\n</div>\n<p>應屆港姐冠軍倪樂琳、亞軍梁嘉莹及友誼小姐王汛文昨晚（11日）參與慈善晚宴，倪樂琳指昨日是季軍楊梓瑤22歲正日生日，但因對方家中有事，所以請了兩星期假回荷蘭，現在唯有等到她返港後再買蛋糕跟對方慶祝。\n\n</p><h2>感激對手孔德賢帶入戲</h2>\n<p>倪樂琳早前曾參加TVB演戲班，事後亦上載上堂短片到社交網，片中她七情上面兼爆喊，她直言首次演戲與想像中不同，是會好激動，又自爆喊完後抽離不到，唔開心了一整天，但也很感激對手孔德賢帶她入戲：「其實都做咗兩次，第一次冇喊，情緒未到位，為演戲而演戲，第二次老師畀咗啲小貼士之後就真係入咗去（戲），我哋兩個就真情流露咁喊！」\n\n<article class=\"align-center\">\n<div class=\"js-media-library-item-preview\">\n<div class=\"field field--name-thumbnail field--type-image field--label-hidden field--item\" data-quickedit-field-id=\"media/4191104/thumbnail/zh-hant/media_library\"> <img alt=\"應屆港姐冠軍倪樂琳、亞軍梁嘉莹及友誼小姐王汛文昨晚參與慈善晚宴。\" class=\"img-responsive\" src=\"https://image.hkhl.hk/f/1024p0/0x0/100/none/3741be06d89b188541962aa5481712e9/2025-04/WhatsApp_Image_2025-04-11_at_10_53_41_PM_1_.jpeg\" typeof=\"foaf:Image\" width=\"100%\"/>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"img_caption\">\n      應屆港姐冠軍倪樂琳、亞軍梁嘉莹及友誼小姐王汛文昨晚參與慈善晚宴。\n    </div>\n</article>\n<article class=\"align-center\">\n<div class=\"js-media-library-item-preview\">\n<div class=\"field field--name-thumbnail field--type-image field--label-hidden field--item\" data-quickedit-field-id=\"media/4191105/thumbnail/zh-hant/media_library\"> <img alt=\"季軍楊梓瑤因對方家中有事，所以請了兩星期假回荷蘭。\" class=\"img-responsive\" src=\"https://image.hkhl.hk/f/1024p0/0x0/100/none/43778f78a4140d4ee9ac04ad794e57c3/2025-04/WhatsApp_Image_2025-04-11_at_10_53_42_PM.jpeg\" typeof=\"foaf:Image\" width=\"100%\"/>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"img_caption\">\n      季軍楊梓瑤因對方家中有事，所以請了兩星期假回荷蘭。\n    </div>\n</article>\n<article class=\"align-center\">\n<div class=\"js-media-library-item-preview\">\n<div class=\"field field--name-thumbnail field--type-image field--label-hidden field--item\" data-quickedit-field-id=\"media/4191111/thumbnail/zh-hant/media_library\"> <img alt=\"倪樂琳早前曾參加TVB演戲班，自爆喊完後抽離不到。\" class=\"img-responsive\" src=\"https://image.hkhl.hk/f/1024p0/0x0/100/none/ca23fd4ef76f647faeb81b9358956fbf/2025-04/WhatsApp_Image_2025-04-11_at_10_53_40_PM.jpeg\" typeof=\"foaf:Image\" width=\"100%\"/>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"img_caption\">\n      倪樂琳早前曾參加TVB演戲班，自爆喊完後抽離不到。\n    </div>\n</article>\n<article class=\"align-center\">\n<div class=\"js-media-library-item-preview\">\n<div class=\"field field--name-thumbnail field--type-image field--label-hidden field--item\" data-quickedit-field-id=\"media/4191112/thumbnail/zh-hant/media_library\"> <img alt=\"梁嘉莹被爆好大懵。\" class=\"img-responsive\" src=\"https://image.hkhl.hk/f/1024p0/0x0/100/none/f3ca611cc1478dee39e1736b78acb41b/2025-04/WhatsApp_Image_2025-04-11_at_10_53_41_PM.jpeg\" typeof=\"foaf:Image\" width=\"100%\"/>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"img_caption\">\n      梁嘉莹被爆好大懵。\n    </div>\n</article>\n<article class=\"align-center\">\n<div class=\"js-media-library-item-preview\">\n<div class=\"field field--name-thumbnail field--type-image field--label-hidden field--item\" data-quickedit-field-id=\"media/4191117/thumbnail/zh-hant/media_library\"> <img alt=\"王汛文指因一直覺得演戲很難，所以也想去嘗試。\" class=\"img-responsive\" src=\"https://image.hkhl.hk/f/1024p0/0x0/100/none/af19f8084076e980ae9a2982ccb75212/2025-04/WhatsApp_Image_2025-04-11_at_10_53_41_PM_0.jpeg\" typeof=\"foaf:Image\" width=\"100%\"/>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"img_caption\">\n      王汛文指因一直覺得演戲很難，所以也想去嘗試。\n    </div>\n</article>\n</p><h3>唔介意做諧星</h3>\n<p>問到抽離不到會否被嚇怕而不敢演戲，她就表示不會，仍很想拍戲，笑言不想被人發現她搞笑的一面，自己選港姐並不是想做諧星，至於梁嘉莹及王汛文亦表示想去上堂，王汛文指因一直覺得演戲很難，所以也想去嘗試，梁嘉莹則本來上次有份，但因要拜山所以沒有去，要等公司再安排，自己對演戲亦有興趣，什麼角色也想試，問她是否可做諧星？倪樂琳搶答表示四人可一齊做，問她們誰人平日比較多烏龍事？倪樂琳及王汛文即彈開，笑指是梁嘉莹及楊梓瑤比較大懵，但她們也是可愛的懵，提到她與《愛‧回家之開心速遞》的「Rebecca」沈可欣撞樣，倪樂琳笑指有很多網民也叫她去做對方的細妹：「可以入到《愛·回家》都幾好，但唔可以有搞笑劇情，要做正經。（有偶包？）因為平時私底下已經係搞笑形象，難得選港姐高貴優雅，我成世都唔做搞笑！」\n\n\n\n</p>\n<div class=\"in-article-banner\">\n<div class=\"mx-auto web\" data-slot=\"inarticlebanner,2,1\" id=\"inarticlebanner2\"></div>\n<div class=\"mx-auto mweb\" data-slot=\"inarticlebanner,2,2\" id=\"inarticlebanner2-MWeb\"></div>\n</div>\n</div>",
