        {
            "title": "曼聯友賽主辦方與約基訪文體旅局  羅淑佩趁機表達冀紅魔鬼「夫添」上陣︱KellyOnline",
            "description": "<div class=\"video paragraphs medium\">\n<p> <figure class=\"margin-top-1\">\n<img alt=\"主辦方連同曼聯名宿約基星期五（11日）訪文體旅局。羅淑佩fb\" class=\"size-full w-100\" src=\"https://image.stheadline.com/f/680p0/0x0/100/none/f3c74d79ea0863487e6b94e86d93b33f/stheadline/inewsmedia/20250412/_2025041212141732345.jpg\"/>\n<figcaption class=\"caption-text\">主辦方連同曼聯名宿約基星期五（11日）訪文體旅局。羅淑佩fb</figcaption>\n</figure>\n</p>\n<div class=\"in-article-banner\">\n<div class=\"mx-auto web\" data-slot=\"inarticlebanner,1,1\" id=\"inarticlebanner1\"></div>\n<div class=\"mx-auto mweb\" data-slot=\"inarticlebanner,1,2\" id=\"inarticlebanner1-MWeb\"></div>\n</div>\n<p>曼聯時隔12年訪港，將在5月30日於香港大球場友賽港足。文化體育及旅遊局局長羅淑佩表示，已趁機向主辦方表達渴望見到紅魔「夫添」（full team）上陣的強烈意願。\n\n</p>\n<p>羅淑佩在社交平台表示，由於星期四（10日）要出席立法會特別財委會，所以不能出席曼聯訪港的記招，幸好主辦方連同曼聯名宿約基（Dwight Yorke）星期五（11日）訪文體旅局，她已趁機會向他們表達渴望見到紅魔「夫添」（full team）上陣的強烈意願。\n\n<article class=\"align-center\" data-watermark-position=\"\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__preview js-media-library-item-preview\">\n<div class=\"field field--name-thumbnail field--type-image field--label-hidden field__item\" data-quickedit-field-id=\"media/4191074/thumbnail/zh-hant/media_library\"> <img alt=\"羅淑佩與約基一齊手執一件印有「Hong Kong」及比賽日期5月30日的曼聯球衣的合照。羅淑佩fb\" class=\"image-style-medium\" src=\"https://image.hkhl.hk/f/1024p0/0x0/100/none/eea2a049b6b6aaa1c6ff4e7e3e216227/2025-04/486128860_10171185083940603_7360790683290182820_n.jpg\" typeof=\"foaf:Image\" width=\"100%\"/>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"media-library-item__attributes\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__name\">\n        羅淑佩與約基一齊手執一件印有「Hong Kong」及比賽日期5月30日的曼聯球衣的合照。羅淑佩fb\n      </div>\n</div>\n</article>\n<article class=\"align-center\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__preview js-media-library-item-preview\">\n<div class=\"field field--name-thumbnail field--type-image field--label-hidden field__item\" data-quickedit-field-id=\"media/4191075/thumbnail/zh-hant/media_library\"> <img alt=\"曼聯下月將會展開首次季尾巡迴賽。曼聯官網截圖\" class=\"image-style-medium\" src=\"https://image.hkhl.hk/f/1024p0/0x0/100/none/c341f89cce869fa6d6c9405c9e0a8f8d/2025-04/123a.jpg\" typeof=\"foaf:Image\" width=\"100%\"/>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"media-library-item__attributes\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__name\">\n        曼聯下月將會展開首次季尾巡迴賽。曼聯官網截圖\n      </div>\n</div>\n</article>\n<article class=\"align-center\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__preview js-media-library-item-preview\">\n<div class=\"field field--name-thumbnail field--type-image field--label-hidden field__item\" data-quickedit-field-id=\"media/4191076/thumbnail/zh-hant/media_library\"> <img alt=\"曼聯下月將會展開首次季尾巡迴賽。曼聯官網截圖\" class=\"image-style-medium\" src=\"https://image.hkhl.hk/f/1024p0/0x0/100/none/461c4eee06acc6e0204737d6c9a6c832/2025-04/234_0.png\" typeof=\"foaf:Image\" width=\"100%\"/>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"media-library-item__attributes\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__name\">\n        曼聯下月將會展開首次季尾巡迴賽。曼聯官網截圖\n      </div>\n</div>\n</article>\n<article class=\"align-center\" data-watermark-position=\"\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__preview js-media-library-item-preview\">\n<div class=\"field field--name-thumbnail field--type-image field--label-hidden field__item\" data-quickedit-field-id=\"media/4191077/thumbnail/zh-hant/media_library\"> <img alt=\"曼聯於5月30日在大球場對港足，翌日離港。盧江球攝\" class=\"image-style-medium\" src=\"https://image.hkhl.hk/f/1024p0/0x0/100/none/3db0cbc5074c8278f2e06db443d6fb34/2025-04/WhatsApp_Image_2025-04-10_at_15_56_51_0_0.jpeg\" typeof=\"foaf:Image\" width=\"100%\"/>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"media-library-item__attributes\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__name\">\n        曼聯於5月30日在大球場對港足，翌日離港。盧江球攝\n      </div>\n</div>\n</article>\n<article class=\"align-center\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__preview js-media-library-item-preview\">\n<div class=\"field field--name-thumbnail field--type-image field--label-hidden field__item\" data-quickedit-field-id=\"media/4191078/thumbnail/zh-hant/media_library\"> <img alt=\"曼聯將在5月30日於香港大球場友賽港足。資料圖片\" class=\"image-style-medium\" src=\"https://image.hkhl.hk/f/1024p0/0x0/100/none/990ba7d0d1c1cef50aac0928813d2847/2025-04/1744277084456-1_0.jpg\" typeof=\"foaf:Image\" width=\"100%\"/>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"media-library-item__attributes\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__name\">\n        曼聯將在5月30日於香港大球場友賽港足。資料圖片\n      </div>\n</div>\n</article>\n</p>\n<p>羅淑佩又稱，昨日見到約基仍然十分「fit」，談及曼聯近期幾場和波，她更向他「哭波喪」說：「如果曼聯前鋒的把握力如約基當年，球隊處境應該大不相同吧！」\n\n</p>\n<p>羅淑佩並上載與約基一齊手執一件印有「Hong Kong」及5月30日比賽日期的曼聯球衣合照。\n\n\n\n</p>\n<div class=\"in-article-banner\">\n<div class=\"mx-auto web\" data-slot=\"inarticlebanner,2,1\" id=\"inarticlebanner2\"></div>\n<div class=\"mx-auto mweb\" data-slot=\"inarticlebanner,2,2\" id=\"inarticlebanner2-MWeb\"></div>\n</div>\n</div>",
