            "title": "譚輝智將到桂林開演唱會準備同太太「搵食」 爆仔女似自己愛食薯片煎炸嘢",
            "description": "<div class=\"video paragraphs medium\">\n<p> <figure class=\"margin-top-1\">\n<img alt=\"譚輝智將到桂林開演唱會準備同太太「搵食」  爆仔女似自己愛食薯片煎炸嘢\" class=\"size-full w-100\" src=\"https://image.stheadline.com/f/680p0/0x0/100/none/8a63886e03b0b1d0619a2a4aba1ca27c/stheadline/inewsmedia/20250412/_2025041211281260626.jpg\"/>\n<figcaption class=\"caption-text\">譚輝智將到桂林開演唱會準備同太太「搵食」  爆仔女似自己愛食薯片煎炸嘢</figcaption>\n</figure>\n</p>\n<div class=\"in-article-banner\">\n<div class=\"mx-auto web\" data-slot=\"inarticlebanner,1,1\" id=\"inarticlebanner1\"></div>\n<div class=\"mx-auto mweb\" data-slot=\"inarticlebanner,1,2\" id=\"inarticlebanner1-MWeb\"></div>\n</div>\n<p>譚輝智昨晚（11日）出席慈善晚宴，剛去完美加登台的他表示今次去的行程都是首次去，所以覺得好開心，又謂一直以來去美國也是自己的夢想，因年紀大怕不能坐那麼長時間飛機，故難得有工作之餘，也算是實現了夢想。譚輝智指因當地也有很多華人看《中年好聲音》和看TVB長大，所以大家也很熱情，又表示自己很喜歡加拿大，之後也考慮帶小朋友一起去旅行。\n\n</p><h2>從比賽到現在瘦了20多磅</h2>\n<article class=\"align-center\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__preview js-media-library-item-preview\">\n<div class=\"field field--name-thumbnail field--type-image field--label-hidden field__item\"> <img alt=\"譚輝智剛去完美加登台，他覺得好開心。\" class=\"image-style-medium\" src=\"https://image.hkhl.hk/f/1024p0/0x0/100/none/a41d87a95b99c6d7bdf934adff83e973/2025-04/WhatsApp_Image_2025-04-11_at_10_53_43_PM_1_.jpeg\" typeof=\"foaf:Image\" width=\"100%\"/>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"media-library-item__attributes\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__name\">\n        譚輝智剛去完美加登台，他覺得好開心。\n      </div>\n</div>\n</article>\n<article class=\"align-center\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__preview js-media-library-item-preview\">\n<div class=\"field field--name-thumbnail field--type-image field--label-hidden field__item\"> <img alt=\"譚輝智指當地也有很多華人看《中年好聲音》和看TVB長大。\" class=\"image-style-medium\" src=\"https://image.hkhl.hk/f/1024p0/0x0/100/none/72ac8cdb658d102105b82b848b9e5639/2025-04/WhatsApp_Image_2025-04-11_at_10_53_43_PM.jpeg\" typeof=\"foaf:Image\" width=\"100%\"/>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"media-library-item__attributes\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__name\">\n        譚輝智指當地也有很多華人看《中年好聲音》和看TVB長大。\n      </div>\n</div>\n</article>\n<article class=\"align-center\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__preview js-media-library-item-preview\">\n<div class=\"field field--name-thumbnail field--type-image field--label-hidden field__item\"> <img alt=\"輝智將會隨旅行團到桂林開演唱會。\" class=\"image-style-medium\" src=\"https://image.hkhl.hk/f/1024p0/0x0/100/none/3738e74d21a0a1be2862e85e6c05bf48/2025-04/WhatsApp_Image_2025-04-11_at_10_53_44_PM.jpeg\" typeof=\"foaf:Image\" width=\"100%\"/>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"media-library-item__attributes\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__name\">\n        輝智將會隨旅行團到桂林開演唱會。\n      </div>\n</div>\n</article>\n<article class=\"align-center\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__preview js-media-library-item-preview\">\n<div class=\"field field--name-thumbnail field--type-image field--label-hidden field__item\"> <img alt=\"今次將會在當地逗留3、4日。\" class=\"image-style-medium\" src=\"https://image.hkhl.hk/f/1024p0/0x0/100/none/cc8876fb9e37115a91bc032e227bdf1f/2025-04/WhatsApp_Image_2025-04-11_at_10_53_44_PM_1_.jpeg\" typeof=\"foaf:Image\" width=\"100%\"/>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"media-library-item__attributes\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__name\">\n        今次將會在當地逗留3、4日。\n      </div>\n</div>\n</article>\n<article class=\"align-center\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__preview js-media-library-item-preview\">\n<div class=\"field field--name-thumbnail field--type-image field--label-hidden field__item\"> <img alt=\"他表示與太太也喜歡食，所以兩公婆到時會去看風景和「搵食」。\" class=\"image-style-medium\" src=\"https://image.hkhl.hk/f/1024p0/0x0/100/none/84329acf28aaf57882ea6d7634b51895/2025-04/WhatsApp_Image_2025-04-11_at_10_53_44_PM_2_.jpeg\" typeof=\"foaf:Image\" width=\"100%\"/>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"media-library-item__attributes\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__name\">\n        他表示與太太也喜歡食，所以兩公婆到時會去看風景和「搵食」。\n      </div>\n</div>\n</article>\n<article class=\"align-center\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__preview js-media-library-item-preview\">\n<div class=\"field field--name-thumbnail field--type-image field--label-hidden field__item\"> <img alt=\"輝智又指從比賽到現在瘦了20多磅。\" class=\"image-style-medium\" src=\"https://image.hkhl.hk/f/1024p0/0x0/100/none/9d5b5974387c58bea155b343f8f2aff2/2025-04/WhatsApp_Image_2025-04-11_at_10_53_44_PM_3_.jpeg\" typeof=\"foaf:Image\" width=\"100%\"/>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"media-library-item__attributes\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__name\">\n        輝智又指從比賽到現在瘦了20多磅。\n      </div>\n</div>\n</article>\n<article class=\"align-center\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__preview js-media-library-item-preview\">\n<div class=\"field field--name-thumbnail field--type-image field--label-hidden field__item\"> <img alt=\"輝智與靚老婆都鍾意食嘢。\" class=\"image-style-medium\" src=\"https://image.hkhl.hk/f/1024p0/0x0/100/none/7d260c9171394bead6be885cf41086b6/2025-04/WhatsApp_Image_2025-04-12_at_11_19_47_AM_1_.jpeg\" typeof=\"foaf:Image\" width=\"100%\"/>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"media-library-item__attributes\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__name\">\n        輝智與靚老婆都鍾意食嘢。\n      </div>\n</div>\n</article>\n<p>提到下星期他將會隨旅行團到桂林開演唱會，而接載觀眾的高鐵列車名字改成「輝智號高鐵專列」，譚輝智就表示這是旅行社的貼心服務，而今次將會在當地逗留3、4日，全家人連親戚朋友也會一起去支持，笑指到時會有「幾圍枱」是自己人，又指太太很喜歡去旅行，加上兩人也喜歡食，所以兩公婆到時會去看風景和「搵食」，問到他是否要keep身形？譚輝智指從比賽到現在瘦了20多磅：「我冇特別減，可能多嘢做我自然就會瘦，不過我戒咗零食，以前好鍾意食薯片，可能唔想小朋友食，佢哋似我，見到煎炸嘢就好開胃。」\n\n\n\n</p>\n<div class=\"in-article-banner\">\n<div class=\"mx-auto web\" data-slot=\"inarticlebanner,2,1\" id=\"inarticlebanner2\"></div>\n<div class=\"mx-auto mweb\" data-slot=\"inarticlebanner,2,2\" id=\"inarticlebanner2-MWeb\"></div>\n</div>\n</div>",
