        {
            "title": "葵涌石籬一邨女子墮山坡被困 頭傷血流披面 消防救下送院",
            "description": "<div class=\"video paragraphs medium\">\n<p> <figure class=\"margin-top-1\">\n<img alt=\"女事主血流披面經包紮後送院敷治。\" class=\"size-full w-100\" src=\"https://image.stheadline.com/f/680p0/0x0/100/none/33d1d9c82acdf3e8c6c36444a1490872/stheadline/inewsmedia/20250412/_2025041211445642767.jpg\"/>\n<figcaption class=\"caption-text\">女事主血流披面經包紮後送院敷治。</figcaption>\n</figure>\n</p>\n<div class=\"in-article-banner\">\n<div class=\"mx-auto web\" data-slot=\"inarticlebanner,1,1\" id=\"inarticlebanner1\"></div>\n<div class=\"mx-auto mweb\" data-slot=\"inarticlebanner,1,2\" id=\"inarticlebanner1-MWeb\"></div>\n</div>\n<p>葵涌石籬（一）邨石逸樓對開，今（12日）早上10時06分，一名女子疑由護土牆墮下被困山坡，消防員接報到場，利用「貓梯」協助事主返回安全位置。\n\n<article class=\"align-center\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__preview js-media-library-item-preview\">\n<div class=\"field field--name-thumbnail field--type-image field--label-hidden field__item\" data-quickedit-field-id=\"media/4191107/thumbnail/zh-hant/media_library\"> <img alt=\"消防用貓梯協助女事主返回安全位置。\" class=\"image-style-medium\" src=\"https://image.hkhl.hk/f/1024p0/0x0/100/none/c08eae77e57d75b289c9ae085d7c729f/2025-04/28a98f55-b52d-42fe-9865-28580ba0d17b.jpg\" typeof=\"foaf:Image\" width=\"100%\"/>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"media-library-item__attributes\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__name\">\n        消防用貓梯協助女事主返回安全位置。\n      </div>\n</div>\n</article>\n<article class=\"align-center\" data-watermark-position=\"\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__preview js-media-library-item-preview\">\n<div class=\"field field--name-thumbnail field--type-image field--label-hidden field__item\" data-quickedit-field-id=\"media/4191108/thumbnail/zh-hant/media_library\"> <img alt=\"消防陪同女傷者落山。\" class=\"image-style-medium\" src=\"https://image.hkhl.hk/f/1024p0/0x0/100/none/a54257f3b42bf2cdcd0084613529cd01/2025-04/56a99c4c-b763-4e78-8f52-9bf372b2928d.jpg\" typeof=\"foaf:Image\" width=\"100%\"/>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"media-library-item__attributes\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__name\">\n        消防陪同女傷者落山。\n      </div>\n</div>\n</article>\n<article class=\"align-center\" data-watermark-position=\"\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__preview js-media-library-item-preview\">\n<div class=\"field field--name-thumbnail field--type-image field--label-hidden field__item\" data-quickedit-field-id=\"media/4191109/thumbnail/zh-hant/media_library\"> <img alt=\"女事主頭傷送院治理。\" class=\"image-style-medium\" src=\"https://image.hkhl.hk/f/1024p0/0x0/100/none/9423ecb3c91c9ce3419b84fea00dbc91/2025-04/c8497ecb-751f-4570-ace2-c46302eeafbd.jpg\" typeof=\"foaf:Image\" width=\"100%\"/>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"media-library-item__attributes\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__name\">\n        女事主頭傷送院治理。\n      </div>\n</div>\n</article>\n<article class=\"align-center\" data-watermark-position=\"\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__preview js-media-library-item-preview\">\n<div class=\"field field--name-thumbnail field--type-image field--label-hidden field__item\" data-quickedit-field-id=\"media/4191110/thumbnail/zh-hant/media_library\"> <img alt=\"消防用貓梯協助女事主返回安全位置。\" class=\"image-style-medium\" src=\"https://image.hkhl.hk/f/1024p0/0x0/100/none/b87395d375cf14ad4619be907d1b1c17/2025-04/c40550bb-8fbf-4e96-a3dc-bf2414c2d4e5.jpg\" typeof=\"foaf:Image\" width=\"100%\"/>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"media-library-item__attributes\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__name\">\n        消防用貓梯協助女事主返回安全位置。\n      </div>\n</div>\n</article>\n</p>\n<p>女事主頭部受傷，血流披臉，衣衫染血，仍然清醒，她經初步包紮後，由消防員及家屬陪同落山，再由救護車送院治理。\n\n\n\n</p>\n<div class=\"in-article-banner\">\n<div class=\"mx-auto web\" data-slot=\"inarticlebanner,2,1\" id=\"inarticlebanner2\"></div>\n<div class=\"mx-auto mweb\" data-slot=\"inarticlebanner,2,2\" id=\"inarticlebanner2-MWeb\"></div>\n</div>\n</div>",
            "link": "https://std.stheadline.com/realtime/article/2063520/即時-港聞-葵涌石籬一邨女子墮山坡被困-頭傷血流披面-消防救下送院",
